==Relation to Dirichlet L-functions==
For rational values of formula_117 (that is, for formula_118 for some integers &quot;p&quot; and &quot;q&quot;), the function formula_119 can be understood to represent a periodic orbit of an element in the cyclic group, and thus formula_120 can be expressed as a simple sum involving the Hurwitz zeta function. This allows relations between certain Dirichlet L-functions to be easily computed.

